citeinfo.origin: City of San Antonio, Planning and Community Development Department
citeinfo.title: Libraries

descript.abstract: This is a graphical point dataset depicting the location of the branch libraries of San Antonio, Texas.
descript.purpose: The City of San Antonio libraries dataset defines the location of branch libraries and provides a representation of such points for the purpose of defining the sites of the San Antonio Public Library System's branch facilities.
descript.supplinf: This metadata describes the dataset libraries; the manner in which the dataset is named on the City of San Antonio's GIS Mapping Application.

timeperd.current: The currentness of the library points are based on ground conditions as of 2003 Aerial photography
